What's that story?

13:48.920 --> 13:53.038
He must have a diarrhea.
It may be confused with a smile,

13:53.100 --> 13:54.430
But it's not. It's just a grin.

13:54.600 --> 13:55.669
Look.

13:56.340 --> 13:59.749
