14:21.200 --> 14:23.350
- Uh... like that.

14:23.720 --> 14:25.278
- You do not know?

14:25.640 --> 14:27.517
6 feet should suffice.

14:27.880 --> 14:29.438
The noose is all ready.

14:29.600 --> 14:32.075
Just put your head through it.
Here, it's a gift. My pleasure.

14:35.200 --> 14:38.397
How can that be? He smiles?
- It was a pleasure to see

14:38.760 --> 14:40.159
