- So?

51:57.160 --> 51:58.354
- It's up to you.

52:00.560 --> 52:04.030
- Wow...
- So you like it?

52:09.680 --> 52:10.635
- Marilyn, tell me...

52:11.000 --> 52:15.790
where did you get these bubbles?
- Alan gave them to me.

52:25.040 --> 52:26.678
Oh, but...

52:28.640 --> 52:29.595
Shit...

52:32.280 --> 52:34.635
- But what is it?

52:35.960 --> 52:37.154
- Uh, nothing.

52:37.520 --> 52:39.192
- I felt like a slap.

52:41.840 --> 52:42.829
You were dreaming.
Go back to sleep.

53:17.240 --> 53:19.276
- This thing is heavy.

53:21.080 --> 53:23.594
- Come on...
But shut up.

53:43.200 --> 53:44.315
Hide yourself.

54:07.040 --> 54:09.235
- What's this racket?

54:19.040 --> 54:20.314
But what...

54:35.200 --> 54:36.428
- But what's

54:36.800 --> 54:38.836
this thing?
Mom!

54:39.200 --> 54:40.599
What's going on?

54:45.520 --> 54:46.714
- It is Alan.

54:51.040 --> 54:53.713
Vincent, help me!

55:25.400 --> 55:26.355
- In here...

55:31.200 --> 55:33.270
- Attention, behind you...

55:33.640 --> 55:34.834
Attention, Alan!

55:35.960 --> 55:37.313
Give me that!

55:45.000 --> 55:46.149
- Come on guys!

55:57.680 --> 55:58.635
- I got it.

56:01.760 --> 56:04.354
Oh no...

56:05.680 --> 56:07.238
- Come here, you!

56:11.800 --> 56:13.392
Oh no!

56:20.060 --> 56:24.120
Go back home ladies and gentlemen,
We have nothing left to sell.

56:26.320 --> 56:28.595
- Goodbye, ma'am.
- Goodbye.

56:28.840 --> 56:32.799
- It's okay Ms. Tuvache, 
we will suicide another time.

56:38.240 --> 56:41.550
- By the way, what do you need?

56:41.800 --> 56:44.997
- Nothing, miss.
Not anymore.

56:46.600 --> 56:50.036
Madam, I ask you
the hand of your daughter.

56:50.400 --> 56:52.152
I don't know her name...

56:52.400 --> 56:53.879
- Marilyn.
- Marilyn.

56:54.120 --> 56:56.714
And with whom I just fell in love,

56:56.960 --> 56:59.315
and who restored my appetite for life.

57:00.560 --> 57:01.515
- Yeah...

57:01.880 --> 57:04.917
- Mom, please,
say yes...

57:06.720 --> 57:11.191
- Well... yes...
But on one condition.

57:11.560 --> 57:13.278
- Anything you want.

57:13.640 --> 57:17.235
That you help us to clean up
all this mess.

57:17.600 --> 57:18.396
- Mom,

57:18.760 --> 57:21.718
I love you.
Me too, I love you.

57:30.960 --> 57:34.589
- I intended to leave this earth

57:36.160 --> 57:37.991
Horrible and evil

57:40.200 --> 57:44.273
To fall asleep with ether

57:44.640 --> 57:48.428
But against all odds

57:48.800 --> 57:52.475
It fell on me

57:53.360 --> 57:58.275
Of course without warning

57:58.640 --> 58:01.029
I never received

58:01.400 --> 58:04.836
Such a look from a girl

58:08.960 --> 58:11.758
- The charms of destiny

58:12.000 --> 58:14.719
have unpredictable twists and turns.

58:17.680 --> 58:21.878
- I saw everything in black

58:22.120 --> 58:25.510
It's nothing to say it.

58:25.880 --> 58:30.510
I was in despair

58:30.880 --> 58:34.634
And who would have predicted

58:35.360 --> 58:37.920
That love would come

58:39.360 --> 58:42.318
In this obscure shop

58:42.680 --> 58:46.070
A cheerful young man

58:48.040 --> 58:49.917
Wearing pretty face

58:55.000 --> 58:57.309
- The charms of destiny

58:57.680 --> 59:00.399
have unpredictable twists and turns.

59:04.000 --> 59:06.230
- No more wasted nights

59:08.200 --> 59:11.237
No more days of suffering

59:12.440 --> 59:14.874
Let's live in the wonder

59:17.040 --> 59:20.794
of a common attraction

59:21.040 --> 59:24.396
All is allowed so long

59:24.760 --> 59:28.594
As love blooms.

59:28.960 --> 59:31.838
Dawn after dawn

59:33.960 --> 59:38.590
Life will follow its course.

59:40.720 --> 59:43.757
The charms of destiny

59:44.000 --> 59:48.437
will perfume our days.

59:51.000 --> 59:52.991
But how did you?

59:54.520 --> 59:56.078
It is so clean

59:56.440 --> 01:00:00.319
we could eat on the floor
- I was going to propose it.

01:00:00.680 --> 01:00:03.478
I am Breton and
I make perfect crêpes.

01:00:04.840 --> 01:00:08.355
How about a crêpe picnic
here, right now?

01:00:08.720 --> 01:00:10.551
Oh yes, why not?

01:00:14.600 --> 01:00:16.272
It's delicious.

01:00:16.640 --> 01:00:18.392
- It's true, crêpes are good.

01:00:18.760 --> 01:00:22.594
- You are a real gem.
- You embarrass me.

01:00:22.960 --> 01:00:24.791
- He is the perfect man.

01:00:35.720 --> 01:00:38.871
What about changing the suicide shop
to a shop for something else?

01:00:39.240 --> 01:00:41.231
- A shop for what?

01:00:41.600 --> 01:00:43.909
- I don't know
we can try.

01:00:44.280 --> 01:00:45.633
Anyway the stock is ruined.

01:00:46.000 --> 01:00:46.989
We could open a crêperie.

01:00:47.360 --> 01:00:49.430
- This is an idea.

01:00:49.680 --> 01:00:54.071
Crêpe evoke mourning.
The clients will not be disoriented.

01:00:56.240 --> 01:00:58.037
- What is this shit?

01:00:58.400 --> 01:00:59.719
- I forgot about him!

01:01:00.080 --> 01:01:01.832
-Someone can explain?

01:01:11.080 --> 01:01:12.957
- It's me Dad.
Everything is my fault.

01:01:22.280 --> 01:01:23.918
Attention, move over!

01:01:33.080 --> 01:01:34.195
Pardon me, madam.

01:01:41.440 --> 01:01:43.874
Mishima, stop it now!

01:01:52.680 --> 01:01:54.272
- Calm down, Dad.

01:01:54.640 --> 01:01:57.234
- I'll explain.
- You will explain nothing!

01:02:07.000 --> 01:02:08.797
Come here, bastard!

01:02:51.080 --> 01:02:53.548
Mishima, if you kill this child,

01:02:53.920 --> 01:02:55.114
I kill myself!

01:02:58.400 --> 01:02:59.913
Please Mishima...

01:03:00.280 --> 01:03:04.592
- Okay, I made a very
big mistake, I'm sorry...

01:03:06.280 --> 01:03:07.030
I beg your pardon.

01:03:09.440 --> 01:03:11.749
I propose a deal.
An honest deal.

01:03:13.320 --> 01:03:16.676
You're a great dad,
the best dad.

01:03:18.320 --> 01:03:21.835
But you're a serious dad,
too serious. Everybody is.

01:03:23.000 --> 01:03:24.752
You never laugh, not even smile.

01:03:31.520 --> 01:03:34.273
So if right here, right now
I can make you laugh,

01:03:34.640 --> 01:03:35.868
you forgive me?

01:03:46.040 --> 01:03:50.716
- Bastard, Mishima! You have the death
of this child on your conscience.

01:03:51.920 --> 01:03:53.478
Oh no...

01:03:53.840 --> 01:03:55.478
- Assassin!

01:03:55.840 --> 01:03:57.478
- But I... I...

01:04:00.000 --> 01:04:01.194
What...

01:04:06.080 --> 01:04:08.355
- He's alive.

01:04:08.600 --> 01:04:09.555
Mom...

01:04:11.640 --> 01:04:12.629
- He's flying.

01:04:20.480 --> 01:04:21.435
Ball.

01:04:24.920 --> 01:04:25.909
You would like?

01:05:44.240 --> 01:05:46.879
One skull-outbreak,
one!

01:06:05.520 --> 01:06:07.033
The "Red Beard" crêpe is for?

01:06:07.400 --> 01:06:08.276
- For me!

01:06:10.720 --> 01:06:12.358
- Thank you.

01:06:16.680 --> 01:06:18.432
- Hello, it's me again.

01:06:21.080 --> 01:06:22.069
- What a good surprise.
What brings you?

01:06:22.440 --> 01:06:24.908
- You would have a...?
- Pardon?

01:06:25.280 --> 01:06:27.589
A cyanide crêpe?

01:06:30.080 --> 01:06:31.513
- Do not move.

01:06:37.200 --> 01:06:38.155
Hold.

01:06:39.120 --> 01:06:42.715
Keep it closed, you fool. If my wife
learnt I still sell those,

01:06:43.080 --> 01:06:44.354
She would kill me.

01:06:44.720 --> 01:06:46.517
- How much?
Nothing.

01:06:46.880 --> 01:06:47.710
- There is no reason

01:06:48.080 --> 01:06:53.200
- It is in memory of the bad
old times. Good day.

01:06:53.560 --> 01:06:54.834
- Thank you.

01:06:57.320 --> 01:06:58.275
- Goodbye madam.

01:06:58.520 --> 01:07:02.479
- Lucrèce, I thought about something.
Yes, what?

01:07:02.720 --> 01:07:04.551
- A loyalty card.

01:07:04.800 --> 01:07:08.031
because now happy
customers come back.

01:07:08.280 --> 01:07:10.999
What do you say?
- Very good idea.

01:07:22.720 --> 01:07:24.278
- Arghh...

01:07:39.040 --> 01:07:44.068
We were stupid.
Today everything is clear.

01:07:44.320 --> 01:07:48.199
Down with morbidity
Since life is splendid.

01:07:49.280 --> 01:07:54.149
Living on homicides
Made us livid

01:07:54.400 --> 01:07:58.279
Let's be lucid
and death to sucide.

01:07:59.200 --> 01:08:04.194
- My face of Lent
I'm tired of it.

01:08:04.440 --> 01:08:08.752
- There is no problem
He's less white

01:08:09.120 --> 01:08:11.429
I love life and even

01:08:11.800 --> 01:08:14.439
- Vincent, we love you

01:08:14.680 --> 01:08:19.196
- I will write poems

01:08:19.560 --> 01:08:24.429
We repainted the world
In a few seconds

01:08:24.800 --> 01:08:26.153
To no longer see

01:08:26.520 --> 01:08:29.432
All these filthy colors

01:08:30.240 --> 01:08:35.154
You are right Alan, 
We must keep the banana.

01:08:35.399 --> 01:08:39.359
Death we are condemning.
You see we are gliding.

01:08:39.720 --> 01:08:42.518
- It's crazy when you think about it.

01:08:42.760 --> 01:08:45.035
A matter of common sense.

01:08:45.399 --> 01:08:47.788
Goodbye violence.

01:08:48.160 --> 01:08:49.957
Deliverance at last.

01:08:50.319 --> 01:08:55.234
And therefore
no more suffering

01:08:55.479 --> 01:08:59.996
The beautiful life starts

01:09:03.319 --> 01:09:05.913
- For us it's over.

01:09:06.279 --> 01:09:10.716
We lost it all.
But we get used to it.

01:09:10.960 --> 01:09:14.032
If we had known

01:09:14.399 --> 01:09:17.278
We would have lived

01:09:17.640 --> 01:09:20.359
As it's evident

01:09:20.720 --> 01:09:25.475
Do not pity us.
You don't know your happiness.

01:09:25.840 --> 01:09:27.990
Being passed away

01:09:28.359 --> 01:09:31.511
Isn't a happy affair.

01:09:31.760 --> 01:09:33.796
An abundance of laughs,
like a perfume

01:09:34.160 --> 01:09:36.627
Which surrounds us.

01:09:36.880 --> 01:09:40.555
The dead season
Isn't our kingdom anymore.

01:09:40.920 --> 01:09:46.392
So we must listen
to all these ghosts.

01:09:46.760 --> 01:09:51.470
All together now
Gloom, go home!

01:09:51.840 --> 01:09:56.436
We listen to you, Miss
We trust you.

01:09:56.800 --> 01:09:59.360
Be natural,

01:09:59.600 --> 01:10:01.591
and without shades.

01:10:01.960 --> 01:10:06.750
- Love spellbinds me,
Sweet romance.

01:10:07.120 --> 01:10:10.715
- It's the universal

01:10:11.080 --> 01:10:14.709
attraction!

01:10:15.080 --> 01:10:17.150
- No dream

01:10:17.520 --> 01:10:19.272
is impossible.

01:10:19.640 --> 01:10:21.471
So long as you believe

01:10:21.840 --> 01:10:24.434
in it strongly.

01:10:24.800 --> 01:10:29.316
And if it's sometimes painful,

01:10:29.680 --> 01:10:32.558
Life is always better
than death.

01:11:51.040 --> 01:11:54.237
- It's all black,
I'm scared. A match?

01:12:01.880 --> 01:12:03.598
- No, don't do that...

